Package: sbplanr
Title: Experimental station-based bicycle sharing planner
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Merlin", "Unterfinger", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "info@munterfinger.ch", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2020-2366"))
URL: https://github.com/munterfi/sbplanr/
BugReports: https://github.com/munterfi/sbplanr/issues/
Description: Tool for placing bicycle sharing stations by iteratively minimizing
    a global energy of a model that reflects the station-based bicycle sharing
    system. The station locations are randomly initialized in the street network
    and iteratively optimized based on the reachable population in combination
    with walking and driving times.
